19 SECTION 1. Arkansas Code ยง 19-8-106(a)(1), concerning the county
20 depository board, is amended to read as follows:
21 (a)(1)(A) The quorum court of each of the several counties shall by
22 ordinance establish a county depository board.
23 (B) The county depository board is to be composed of the
